EMPLOYMENT AGREEMENT

This Employment Agreement ("Agreement") is entered into on June 20, 2026, between TechNova Solutions Private Limited, having its registered office at Hyderabad, Telangana, India ("Employer"), and Harini Reddy ("Employee").

1. POSITION

The Employee shall be employed as a Software Engineer and shall perform duties and responsibilities assigned by the Employer from time to time.

2. COMPENSATION

The Employee shall receive an annual salary of INR 8,00,000 (Eight Lakh Rupees Only), payable in accordance with the Employer's payroll policies and applicable laws.

3. WORKING HOURS

The Employee shall work 40 hours per week. Additional hours may be required to meet project deadlines and business requirements.

4. CONFIDENTIALITY

The Employee shall not disclose any confidential information, trade secrets, customer information, source code, business plans, financial information, or proprietary data belonging to the Employer during or after employment.

5. INTELLECTUAL PROPERTY

Any inventions, software, designs, documentation, algorithms, research, developments, or work products created during employment shall be the exclusive property of the Employer.

6. TERMINATION

Either party may terminate this Agreement by providing thirty (30) days written notice. The Employer may terminate employment immediately in cases of misconduct, fraud, breach of confidentiality, or violation of company policies.

7. NON-COMPETE

The Employee agrees not to work for a direct competitor of the Employer for a period of six (6) months following termination of employment within the same geographic region.

8. GOVERNING LAW

This Agreement shall be governed by and construed in accordance with the laws of India.

